{
  "title": "Mildly Smoky Egyptian Serrano Ham Kebabs",
  "description": "A tangy and chewy Egyptian dish featuring Serrano ham, grilled to perfection on a yakimono grill, suitable for a satvik friendly diet.",
  "cuisine": "Egyptian",
